'''圣米迦勒钟楼'''（St Michael's Tower）位于英格兰[[格洛斯特|格洛斯特]]四条主要街道（东门街、南门街、西门街、北门街）十字路口的东南转角，入口位于南门街。这里也是城市的最高处。它建于1465年，是圣米迦勒堂（''St Michael the Archangel''）的遗迹。<ref name=gct>[https://web.archive.org/web/20120328111804/http://www.gloucestercivictrust.org.uk/gloucester-civic-trust/St-Michaels-Tower.html St Michael’s Tower at Gloucester Cross.] [[Gloucester_Civic_Trust|Gloucester Civic Trust]], 2010. Internet Archive. Retrieved 25 November 2016.</ref> 1952年列为II*级[[登录建筑|登录建筑]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.britishlistedbuildings.co.uk/en-472215-tower-of-the-former-church-of-st-michael#.WLf3vn9DTIU|title=Tower of the Former Church of St Michael, Gloucester|publisher=British Listed Buildings|accessdate=2017-03-02|archive-date=2017-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170302194039/http://www.britishlistedbuildings.co.uk/en-472215-tower-of-the-former-church-of-st-michael#.WLf3vn9DTIU|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==历史==
[[File:Mercers_Hall,_Gloucester.jpg|thumb]]
圣米迦勒堂创建于12世纪，旧教堂已在1840年代拆除，1851年建造新堂，1940年关闭，1956年拆除。堂会并入[[格洛斯特圣玛利亚堂|格洛斯特圣玛利亚堂]].<ref name=gct/> <ref>[https://www.bbc.co.uk/gloucestershire/content/image_galleries/st_michaels_tower_gallery.shtml In Pictures: St. Michael's Tower.] {{Wayback|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/gloucestershire/content/image_galleries/st_michaels_tower_gallery.shtml |date=20140516023403 }} BBC Gloucestershire, August 2008. Retrieved 7 August 2011.</ref>

从1976年至1981年，楼上开设钟博物馆，1985年至1998年，用作旅游信息中心。底楼一度成为东门街和南门街之间的开放式走道。后来用于年久失修，被格洛斯特市议会用作存储空间。<ref name=gct/>2009年，格洛斯特市议会批准将该建筑租赁给格洛斯特公民信托，2010年，该建筑以300，000欧元的费用修复。此后，塔成为公民信托的总部，旨在打造"学习塔"，致力于格洛斯特的历史<ref>[http://www.thisisgloucestershire.co.uk/Gloucester-trust-signs-new-deal/story-11851897-detail/story.html Gloucester trust signs new deal.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.thisisgloucestershire.co.uk/Gloucester-trust-signs-new-deal/story-11851897-detail/story.html |date=20120531074652 }} This is Gloucestershire, 17 December 2009. Retrieved 6 August 2011.</ref>。

2011年8月，公民信托基金发起了一项运动，以恢复钟楼的钟声。<ref>"Let bell ring out again at tower" by Dan Charles in The Citizen, August 2011.</ref> 现已完成<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.keltektrust.org.uk/gloucestersmt.html |title=Keltek Trust web page |access-date=2020-11-28 |archive-date=2016-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161225031226/http://keltektrust.org.uk/gloucestersmt.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

